.Sh DESCRIPTION
.
.Nm VisiData
is a multipurpose tool for exploring, cleaning, editing, and restructuring data from supported sources, including tsv, csv, xlsx, hdf5, and sqlite.
Rows can be selected, filtered, and grouped; columns can be rearranged, transformed, and derived via regex or Python expressions; workflows can be documented, communicated, and replayed via the commandlog.
.Nm VisiData No is built on the
.Sy vdtui No platform.
.
.Sh REPLAY MODE
.Bl -tag -width XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX -compact
.It Fl "p, --play" Ar cmdlog No
.No replays a saved Ar cmdlog.vd No within the interface

.It Fl -batch
replays in batch mode (with no interface and all output to stdout)

.It Fl -delay Ar seconds
.No delays Ar seconds No between commands

.It Fl "o, --output" Ar file No
.No saves the final visible sheet to Ar file No (as .tsv) at the end of the replay

.It Sy While Replaying
.El
.Bl -tag -width XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX -compact -offset XXX
.It Sy ^U
pauses/resumes replay
.It Sy Space
executes next row in the replaying sheet
.El
.Sh MAJOR OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX -compact
.
