.Sh .visidatarc
For customizing
.Nm VisiData
settings which persist across every session.
A sample
.Sy .visidatarc
is:
.Bd -literal
options.color_key_col="cyan"
options.min_memory_mb=100
.Ed

This configures key coloumns to be colored 'cyan' and for visidata to stop loading and async processing unless 100 mb of memory are available.
